codex
I’ve narrowed this to a runtime verifier design: it will attempt the exact `stake` and `unstake` path stages from a zero-funded attacker contract, treat balance deltas as the source of truth, and encode pool-liquidity/revert outcomes as concrete infeasibility. I’m writing that now, then I’ll compile it locally if the toolchain is present.
